        "head": "",
        "format": "/* ===== FULLSCREEN BACKGROUND ===== */\nbody,\nhtml,\n.nrdb-layout,\n.nrdb-layout-main,\n.v-application,\n.v-main,\nmain {\n    background: #0b5d3b !important;\n    margin: 0 !important;\n    padding: 0 !important;\n    overflow: hidden !important;\n}\n\n/* ===== REMOVE TOP BAR COMPLETELY ===== */\n.v-toolbar,\n.v-app-bar,\n.nrdb-layout-header,\nheader,\nnav,\n.v-navigation-drawer {\n    display: none !important;\n}\n\n/* ===== REMOVE GROUP BOX / WHITE CARD ===== */\n.nrdb-ui-group,\n.nrdb-ui-group > div,\n.v-card,\n.v-sheet {\n    background: transparent !important;\n    box-shadow: none !important;\n    border: none !important;\n}\n\n/* ===== REMOVE ALL SPACING ===== */\n.nrdb-layout-main,\n.v-main,\nmain {\n    padding: 0 !important;\n    margin: 0 !important;\n}\n\n/* ===== REMOVE INNER GROUP PADDING ===== */\n.nrdb-ui-group__content,\n.v-card-text {\n    padding: 0 !important;\n    margin: 0 !important;\n}\n\n/* ===== REMOVE ANY OUTLINES ===== */\n* {\n    outline: none !important;\n}\n\n",
